EMPATHY: Sense a target's emotions

Syntax: empathy [at <target>]
        psi empathy [at <target>]

DESCRIPTION:
  Sense the emotional state of a target in the same room. Costs 4 ISP.

  Examples:
    empathy at guard
    psi empathy at merchant

NOTES:
  You must know empathy and have enough ISP.
  In combat, using psionics costs one attack from your APM pool.

SEE ALSO: psi, psionics, telepathy
